data.name: lblBatchHelp.Text
data.value: 1• Send exactly 1 PDF page in each request. GPT processes pages one by one. 2• Send 2 PDF pages together in a single request. GPT can read both pages at once. 3• Send 3 PDF pages at a time. GPT will have three pages’ context. 4• Send 4 PDF pages together so GPT sees more context at once.

data.name: toolTipItem10.Text
data.value:
1 = Send each page individually.
2 = Send two pages in a single GPT query.
3 = Send three pages at once.
4 = Send four pages at time wider context to GPT but not recommanded for medical material.
